<configuration_setting>
    <name_space>COMMERCE/SYSTEM/INVENTORY/inventoryStrategy</name_space>
    <description>Determines the strategy or approach the system uses for inventory behavior. The only valid value is 'allocatedjournaling' (no quotes). Warning: changing this value on a production system can have serious consequences. Please refer to Elastic Path documentation for guidance.</description>
